      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MR. IRRELEVENT (6) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (18.16) in a Mix 3/4 at this track. Has ability and looks hard to stop. REDEMPTIONIST (2) was prominent early off a low draw but weakened and dropped out when 7th over 324m at this track in Grade 5 company. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. KEAON BANNER (4) has found the minor placings here at last couple of runs, finishing second last time beaten 4 lengths (17.88). Speedy beginner who can find the front with a clean break from the middle of the draw. Hard to beat again. SNEAKY GERI (1) jumps at a shorter trip and still warrants respect.",
